        Society.) 

<li><!WA6><a href="http://www.cs.arizona.edu/people/toni/papers/resolution-focs96.ps"> Simplified and improved
        Resolution lower bounds</a>, with Paul Beame.
        <i>Proceedings from Symposium on Foundations of Computer Science</i>,
        to appear.

<li><!WA7><a href="http://www.cs.arizona.edu/people/toni/papers/stconn-focs.ps"> Improved depth lower bounds for
